<inglise> COMMISSION REGULATION (EEC) No 1696/80 of 30 June 1980 fixing, for the 1979/80 marketing year, the maximum amount of the contribution to storage costs which sugar manufacturers may require of beet and cane producers when sugar is carried forward </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (EM&Uuml;) nr 1696/80, millega m&auml;&auml;ratakse 1979/80. turustusaastaks kindlaks laokulude osamaksu &uuml;lemm&auml;&auml;r, mida suhkrutootjad v&otilde;ivad suhkru &uuml;lekandmisel suhkrupeedi ja suhkruroo tootjatelt n&otilde;uda 30. juuni 1980 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 3330/74 of 19 December 1974 on the common organization of the market in sugar (1), as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 1396/78 (2), and in particular Article 31 (4) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 19. detsembri 1974. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 3330/74 suhkruturu &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, (1) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 1396/78, (2) eriti selle artikli 31 l&otilde;iget 4, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 2 of Council Regulation (EEC) No 748/68 (3), as amended by Regulation (EEC) No 2829/71 (4), provides that the sugar manufacturer may require beet or cane sellers to reimburse part of the storage costs up to a maximum amount; whereas such amount must be calculated on the basis of the reimbursement provided for in Article 8 of Regulation (EEC) No 3330/74 and of the percentages referred to in Article 27 (4) and (5) of that Regulation; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: n&otilde;ukogu m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 748/68 (3) (muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 2829/71 (4)) artiklis 2 n&auml;hakse ette, et suhkrutootjad v&otilde;ivad suhkrupeedi v&otilde;i suhkruroo m&uuml;&uuml;jatelt n&otilde;uda osaliselt laokulude tasumist maksimumsumma piires; nimetatud summa tuleb arvutada m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3330/74 artiklis 8 etten&auml;htud h&uuml;vitise ja nimetatud m&auml;&auml;ruse artikli 27 l&otilde;igetes 4 ja 5 osutatud protsentide alusel; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Council Regulation (EEC) No 1594/80 (5) fixed the amount of the reimbursement of storage costs at 0 746 ECU per month per 100 kilograms of white sugar and the percentage referred to above at 60 %; </inglise>
<eesti> n&otilde;ukogu m&auml;&auml;ruses (EM&Uuml;) nr 1594/80 (5) on m&auml;&auml;ratud kindlaks laokulude h&uuml;vitis 0,46 ek&uuml;&uuml;d 100 kg valge suhkru kohta kuus ja eespool nimetatud protsendim&auml;&auml;r 60; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, moreover, the customary terms of purchase for sugar cane in the French overseas departments should be baken into account; </inglise>
<eesti> tuleks v&otilde;tta arvesse suhkruroo ostmise tavap&auml;raseid tingimusi Prantsuse &uuml;lemeredepartemangudes; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the said maximum amount should be fixed per tonne of sugar beet with an assumed yield of 130 kilograms of white sugar and a sugar content of 16 %, and for beet having a sugar content different from that of the standard quality, the same adjustments should be laid down as are provided for in Commission Regulation (EEC) No 2497/69 (6) and Commission Regulation (EEC) No 2571/69 (7); </inglise>
<eesti> nimetatud maksimumsummad tuleks kindlaks m&auml;&auml;rata suhkrupeedi tonni kohta, mille eeldatav saagis on 130 kg valget suhkrut ja mille &uuml;ldsuhkur on 16%, ning suhkrupeedi puhul, mille &uuml;ldsuhkur erineb standardkvaliteediga suhkrupeedi omast, tuleb teha komisjoni m&auml;&auml;rustes (EM&Uuml;) nr 2497/69 (6) ja (EM&Uuml;) nr 2571/69 (7) etten&auml;htud kohandused; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, to facilitate supervision of the carry-forward system envisaged, sugar manufacturers should be required to inform the Member States of the total amounts charged to beet or cane sellers pursuant to Article 2 (1) of Regulation (EEC) No 748/68; </inglise>
<eesti> kavandatava &uuml;lekandmiss&uuml;steemi j&auml;relevalve h&otilde;lbustamiseks tuleb suhkrutootjatelt n&otilde;uda, et nad teavitavad liikmesriike suhkrupeedi v&otilde;i suhkruroo m&uuml;&uuml;jatelt m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 748/68 artikli 2 l&otilde;ikele 1 alusel n&otilde;utud summadest; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the opinion of the Management Committee for Sugar, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las suhkruturu korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> For the 1979/80 sugar marketing year, the maximum amount provided for in Article 2 (1) of Regulation (EEC) No 748/68 shall, per month of storage during the period specified in Article 31 of Regulation (EEC) No 3330/74, be as follows: (a) 0 7359 ECU per tonne of sugar beet having a sugar content of 16 %; </inglise>
<eesti> Suhkru 1979/80. turustusaastal on m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 748/68 artikli 2 l&otilde;ikes 1 etten&auml;htud maksimumsumma &uuml;he ladustuskuu kohta m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3330/74 artiklis 31 t&auml;psustatud ajavahemiku jooksul j&auml;rgmine: a) 0,359 ek&uuml;&uuml;d suhkrupeedi tonni kohta, mille &uuml;ldsuhkur on 16%; </eesti>
<inglise> (b) 0 7276 ECU per quantity of cane required to manufacture 100 kilograms of sugar. </inglise>
<eesti> b) 0,276 ek&uuml;&uuml;d suhkruroo koguse kohta, mida on vaja 100 kg suhkru tootmiseks. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> The amount fixed in paragraph 1 (a) shall as regards beet having a sugar content other than 16 %, be adjusted by the percentages laid down in Regulations (EEC) No 2497/69 and (EEC) No 2571/69. </inglise>
<eesti> L&otilde;ike 1 punktis a kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ratud summat kohandatakse muu kui 16% &uuml;ldsuhkruga suhkrupeedi puhul m&auml;&auml;rustes (EM&Uuml;) nr 2497/69 ja (EM&Uuml;) nr 2571/69 etten&auml;htud protsendim&auml;&auml;radega. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> Any sugar manufacturer who, pursuant to Article 31 of Regulation (EEC) No 3330/74, carries forward part of his production to the following marketing year shall, before 1 June in that marketing year, inform the Member State in whose territory the undertaking in question is situated of the total amounts charged to beet or cane sellers pursuant to Article 2 (1) of Regulation (EEC) No 748/68. </inglise>
<eesti> Iga suhkrutootja, kes kannab m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3330/74 artikli 31 alusel oma toodangu &uuml;le j&auml;rgmisesse turustusaastasse, teatab enne selle turustusaasta 1. juunit liikmesriigile, mille territooriumil k&otilde;nealune ettev&otilde;tja asub, suhkrupeedi ja suhkruroo m&uuml;&uuml;jatelt m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 748/68 artikli 2 l&otilde;ike 1 alusel n&otilde;utud kogusumma. </eesti>
 